Class Height

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.query.client.css.Height
All Implemented Interfaces:
TakesLength, TakesPercentage
public class Height
extends java.lang.Object
implements TakesLength, TakesPercentage

This property specifies the content height of boxes generated by block-level, inline-block and replaced elements. This property does not apply to non-replaced inline-level elements. See the section on computing heights and margins for non-replaced inline elements for the rules used instead.
